He added: besides the formal problems, he did not agree that according to the bill a hundred people were accommodated, since they have only eleven rooms in which not so many people do.
In addition, meals were also included in the bill, while the restaurant has not been working for a long time.
The enthusiastic invoice manufacturers were also not informed that the travel agency chosen in Budapest organizes trips exclusively abroad, so that in the cash payment bill they foolishly indicated as a service a trip within Hungary, which did not coincide with the agency's billing practice.
In addition - as was known during the investigation - VAT also included in the document, although travel outside the territory of the European Union was tax-free.
